      "title": "Dhammika became a minister",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka People's Alliance National List MP Dammika Perera was recently sworn in as the Minister of Investment Promotion in the presence of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa."
      ],
